# Summary
This documentation page explains how to integrate Amplitude Data validation into CI workflows, detailing the process of creating API tokens, configuring environment variables, and running `ampli status` commands using Docker containers in CI systems like GitHub Actions and Bitbucket Pipelines to verify analytics implementations against tracking plans.

